# CNC Programming Fundamentals

## ISO Standard G-Code & M-Code Structured Reference

---

# 1. Introduction

This repository contains structured notes about CNC programming fundamentals using ISO-standard G-code and M-code syntax.

The purpose of this document is to:

* Provide a clean technical reference
* Organize core CNC commands
