# 6. Auxiliary Programming Elements

---

# 6.1 Block Numbering

| Code | Description                         |
| ---- | ----------------------------------- |
| N    | Block number identifier (optional). |

Used for organization and debugging.

---

# 6.2 Tool Selection and Offsets

| Code | Description                          |
| ---- | ------------------------------------ |
| T    | Tool selection command.              |
| M06  | Executes tool change.                |
| D    | Tool diameter or length offset call. |

Important:

* T selects the tool.
* M06 performs the tool change.
* D applies stored tool geometry compensation.

---

# 6.3 Feed and Block Control

| Code | Description                          |
| ---- | ------------------------------------ |
| F    | Feed rate command (Modal).           |
| /    | Block skip.                          |
| ;    | Comment indicator.                   |
| #    | End Of Block (controller dependent). |

